　　日\r\n　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　檢　察　官　林書伃","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1960%2c20220525%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,簡,1960,20220525,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1960","JDATE":"20220525","JTITLE":"妨害名譽"}